thread.title: Diane Delli Colli
thread.title_full: MapsCompany reviewed by Diane Delli Colli

author: Diane Delli Colli
title: Diane Delli Colli
text:
I originally gave a poor review as it took forever to receive my maps after I ordered them. In reality the reason the order was delayed was due to an error on my part. In the end, The MapsCompany actually put a lot of effort in ensuring the delivery to the right address.
5* for customer service and 5* for the actual quality of the map.
Diane
